title: Vampire doll volume 1-4
description: Guilt-Na-Zan is a vampire aristocrat who was sealed into a cross by Kyouji&#039;s ancestor more than 100 years ago. Now Kyouji has revived him--although his soul was resurrected into a cute female doll and can only transform into his real figure when he sucks blood from Kyouji&#039;s sister Tonae... But when you combine Goth clothes and hot vampires, slowly but surely everyone will start to feel like one big family!
